  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI of &gt; 40 kg/m2 or &gt; 35 kg/m2 with obesity-related comorbidities

          -  Failure to achieve sustainable weight loss with proven conservative measures

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe psychiatric and / or eating disorders

          -  unable to keep to a prescribed postoperative diet

          -  &lt; 18 or &gt; 60 years

          -  not eligible to bariatric surgery according to a member of the multidisciplinary team
             (psychologist, dietician, nurse practitioner, general practitioner and surgeon)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
